Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:39.95,logo2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}SGS曙光社\Nhttp://bbs.sgsub.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,契约达成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去已经被改写了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.72,0:01:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请快点到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个浑身是血的人倒在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下 夏罗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个小孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H666666&\b0\pos(319,372)\blur5}怀旧的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏罗被诱拐了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.37,0:02:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后夏罗怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为和犯人的交易成交了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.31,0:02:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交易?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么交易?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘~密~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种程度的混乱倒也是经常的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏罗小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个大笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『没关系』你个头啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是有关系啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特·奈特雷伊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没有杀她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能更早和你达成共识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我设了时间限制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个喜欢收集毒药的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他给了我一些稀罕的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就给她们试了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么连艾可也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个解毒剂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不知是否有效的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不会听我的话了 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖帽子的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我说过想要那个铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过也并不是非拿到不可的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把它销毁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好是谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个铃铛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是艾丽丝的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为阿嵬茨的力量 才变成那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的办法是毁不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,销毁它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用你那能否定与毁灭阿嵬茨力量的疯帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁掉那个铃铛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上给我动手!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我今后能继续活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我要去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能原谅我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪莉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要听他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那是你一直追寻的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了让你活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就满足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特·奈特雷伊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 卖帽子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 快把解毒剂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖帽子的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我最喜欢你这样的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文森特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你的基尔巴特哥哥一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我连自己都保护不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,责任在于我的弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你却为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.52,0:07:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍帅也给我适可而止!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要自作多情了大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了您?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为自己而活的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来救您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我也要保护自己的命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您要是个三长两短
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是会被您的母亲雪莉大人杀掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样…太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了能帮助扎克斯哥哥才来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎克斯 哥哥?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏罗叫布雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎克斯哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 以前就是这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不是真正的兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是把他当哥哥看待了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩过去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了自我介绍了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是雷姆·鲁那特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常去兰玆华斯家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟扎克西斯的交情也有10多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来布雷克也有朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友…朋友 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克有点怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前他就是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前他不擅社交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个无论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连微笑都不会的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到了吗 雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏罗大人发现了一个濒死的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑身起鸡皮疙瘩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要当客人招待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也别接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是一只受伤的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改变他的人 就是雪莉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是夏罗大人的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:10:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是被雪莉大人宽广的胸襟感化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扎克西斯也逐渐敞开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在已经能真正地笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏罗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到笑脸猫的脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是过去被阿嵬茨德意志夺走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.11,0:10:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了他 我想起了很多以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷克在追寻100年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝也在寻找自己的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我呢…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥斯卡叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:10:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制服?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个穿着很合身嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 奥斯卡大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把我们几个带哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们几个才能做到的重要的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这封信是拉特维兹学院寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉特维兹学院?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个国家中位列前三的寄宿制学校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的艾达就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达? 那是个啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有妹妹的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是这封信的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜启 亲爱的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:57.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天气很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天到底是哪一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少应该写上日期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学校的腰子派也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心就把男生弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是粗心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附 我有了喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 喜欢的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事我绝对不允许
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是紧急情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们穿成这样是为了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了确认艾达这封信的真意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们亲自要潜入学校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我按规矩去办个手续啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可没那个时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.14,0:12:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就一点也不浪漫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好～出发出发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就从贝萨流士家秘密建造的地下通道进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是拉特维兹学院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不清楚 不过别抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:28.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海藻头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.38,0:13:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥斯卡大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.72,0:13:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有学生过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 基尔巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的变装是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.24,0:13:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我们是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天气真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这大叔是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是变态?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这也太勉强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是有不明人士闯进学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾略特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和奥兹他们走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 不必担心他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹可是能享受这种状况的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是这样 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该更高兴一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 为了这个才来这里…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么快就找到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校内是禁烟的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你躲起来吸烟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是逃不过这Snow-drop的鼻子!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔他们到底跑哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是蛮开心的 应该没事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是看不出你哪里开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那么不愿见到妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝啊 有时候很敏锐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在表扬你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够见面很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 有点害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥要来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都没做好心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前写信的时候不是提到过奥兹的情况么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:16:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我…都长这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却一点都没变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分开的时候 艾达还很小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定已经记不清我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后都已经10年了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也早已不是从前的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果…如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说 这根本不是艾达…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹可是不会说这种话的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以现在请坦率地表达想见面的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹 你可真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要做我自己就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是骗人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…听了那话…还是有点…高…高兴…的!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:17:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你为什么不按你自己说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别回嘴 你个垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对此你要充满自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪? Snow～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发自肺腑地高喊『我是你的仆人』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快喊 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『我是艾丽丝的仆人』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的和以前一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥很高大 很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比谁都帅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记忆都是会美化的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的哥哥要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然比记忆中要小
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却的确在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以碰触 可以说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见你 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是变了 却没有变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不放手!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我适可而止一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是我的私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么随意扑上来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么仆人啊 笨兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥兹是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别随便把他当成你的私人物品!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海藻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关系好到开始吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会忘了我们的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说大家说的不明人士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是大叔你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀～想见你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很久没有像这样和基尔说话了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有戴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帽子?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到帽子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是艾达送的礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:28.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真的是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔这里有封信 关于『附』的那些我有些疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经做好觉悟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你痛快地死的 基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:20:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:20:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我把话说完
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 奥兹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我一个人丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是又和叔叔他们分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像又回到了从前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 艾达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.64,0:21:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁在弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然大部分重新编排了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:21:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.12,0:22:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这个八音盒是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}少爷的罪孽过于深重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}只是不想把别人卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}纠正主人的言行也是随从的责任哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}不过是自我满足而已!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}会死的。如果只有这个办法我不会迷茫的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.98,0:24:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}少爷是公认的『加害者』
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)\3c&H000000&}根本不懂幸存者的痛苦
